{"pages": [{"words": {"text": ["The", "One", "Advantage", "Leftists", "Cannot", "Possibly", "Claim", "\u201cBetter", "are", "the", "poor", "who", "walk", "in", "integrity", "than", "the", "rich", "who", "are", "perverse", "in", "their", "ways.\u201d", "(Proverbs", "28:6)", "It", "is", "common", "for", "conservatives", "to", "bewail", "the", "wholesale", "systemic", "censorship", "of", "their", "views", "by", "Leftist", "media", "outlets", "including", "the", "\u201calphabet\u201d", "news", "networks", "Amazon,", "Facebook,", "Google,", "and", "Twitter", "to", "name", "a", "few.", "Nevertheless", "there", "is", "one", "thing", "that", "Leftism", "can", "never", "accomplish,", "which", "is", "to", "garner", "genuine", "trust", "in", "its", "message", "by", "people", "who", "are", "committed", "to", "thinking", "critically.", "One", "core", "aspect", "of", "Leftist", "propagandization", "is", "indeed", "censorship", "that", "excludes", "from", "consideration", "certain", "views", "and", "supportive", "data", "that", "are", "decreed,", "for", "unsubstantiated", "reasons,", "to", "be", "faulty.", "Censorship,", "by", "definition,", "contradicts", "scientific", "inquiry", "in", "every", "context,", "including", "its", "demand", "for", "consideration", "of", "every", "relevant", "hypothesis", "and", "consequential", "bit", "of", "data", "in", "the", "determination", "to", "reach", "resolutions", "for", "a", "given", "challenge.", "It", "is", "for", "this", "very", "reason", "that", "Leftism", "can", "never", "tolerate", "the", "exposure", "of", "its", "views", "to", "honest", "analysis", "and", "substantive", "scrutiny.", "This", "is", "also", "why", "President", "Joe", "Biden,", "Vice", "President", "Kamala", "Harris,", "House", "Speaker", "Nancy", "Pelosi,", "and", "Senate", "Majority", "Leader", "Chuck", "Schumer,", "to", "name", "just", "a", "few,", "virtually", "never", "submit", "their", "views", "to", "public", "engagement", "with", "those", "of", "their", "colleagues", "who", "hold", "opposing", "points", "of", "view.", "Since", "it", "is", "Leftists", "who,", "as", "a", "whole,", "parade", "themselves", "as", "\u201cchampions", "of", "science,\u201d", "it", "would", "be", "extremely", "fruitful", "to", "the", "health", "and", "security", "of", "our", "nation\u2019s", "future", "for", "conservatives", "to", "relentlessly", "highlight", "the", "former\u2019s", "moral", "cowardice", "and", "intellectual", "nakedness.", "Indeed,", "they", "ought", "instead", "to", "demand", "renunciation", "of", "their", "glaring", "hypocrisy.", "In", "other", "words,", "instead", "of", "fixating", "on", "the", "deprivation", "that", "Leftism", "seeks", "to", "impose,", "conservatives", "should", "embrace", "the", "opportunity", "to", "use", "the", "voice", "that", "we", "do", "have,", "to", "exposing", "the", "Leftist", "agenda", "for", "what", "it", "is;", "fraudulent", "to", "the", "core.", "No", "advantage", "that", "the", "Left", "is", "seeking", "to", "manipulate", "will", "ever", "successfully", "hide", "the", "reality", "that", "their", "platform", "is", "based", "on", "lies.", "This", "posture", "not", "only", "confounds", "conservatism,", "but", "also", "threaten", "the", "security", "of", "every", "single", "member", "of", "society", "regardless", "of", "their", "place", "on", "the", "political", "spectrum.", "The", "big", "question", "though,", "is", "why", "conservatives", "resist", "seizing", "this", "potentially", "fruitful", "opportunity.", "Gary", "Jensen,", "Pastor", "\u00a9", "March", "16,", "2021", "Holy", "Trinity", "Lutheran", "Church", "(NALC),", "Berlin,", "PA,", "USA"], "bbox": [[0.262974, 0.094457, 0.035224, 0.017727], [0.303327, 0.094457, 0.039377, 0.017727], [0.347879, 0.094457, 0.102029, 0.017727], [0.454984, 0.094457, 0.068271, 0.017727], [0.528441, 0.094457, 0.068082, 0.017727], [0.601693, 0.094457, 0.07712, 0.017727], [0.684036, 0.094457, 0.053349, 0.017727], [0.225523, 0.114381, 0.038225, 0.010152], [0.26672, 0.1